#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:2
#: 7674a5b52d9c4b028e212f8d58dd7694
msgid "Rayleigh-Bénard Convection"
msgstr "瑞利-贝纳德对流"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:4
#: 0fcf0d5792bf40e0905e4ecbe19c3551
msgid ""
"The Rayleigh-Bénard problem couples incompressible fluid flow with heat "
"transport: a horizontal cavity heated from below, cooled from above, "
"develops convective rolls once the buoyancy force exceeds the dissipative "
"effects of viscosity and thermal diffusion. The script "
"``examples/fluid/rayleigh_benard/rayleigh_benard.py`` solves the steady-"
"state Boussinesq approximation in a 2:1 aspect-ratio rectangular cavity at a"
" configurable Rayleigh number."
msgstr ""
"瑞利-贝纳德问题将不可压缩流体流动与热输运耦合在一起：一个底部加热、顶部冷却的水平腔体，一旦浮力超过黏性与热扩散的耗散效应，便会发展出对流卷。脚本 "
"``examples/fluid/rayleigh_benard/rayleigh_benard.py`` 在长宽比为 2:1 "
"的矩形腔体中、以可配置的瑞利数求解稳态布西内斯克近似。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:12
#: 5b3377eeb48b4d1a8a7ea941e55fca40
msgid ""
"This is the only example in :doc:`index` that involves a **multi-physics "
"coupling** — momentum, continuity, and energy in one monolithic system."
msgstr "这是 :doc:`index` 中唯一涉及\\ **多物理场耦合**\\ 的算例——将动量、连续性与能量纳入一个整体系统。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:18
#: d4bf534c40e74d9ea65e78f422642f6f
msgid "Problem"
msgstr "问题"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:20
#: ae6b5b006e6845a7b322c7883daf3b2e
msgid "The Boussinesq equations,"
msgstr "布西内斯克方程组，"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:22
#: ed634075ecf84451a3c913d35ab17cb9
msgid ""
"\\rho\\, (\\mathbf{u} \\cdot \\nabla)\\mathbf{u}\n"
"\\;=\\; -\\nabla p + \\mu\\, \\Delta \\mathbf{u}\n"
"- \\rho\\, g\\, \\beta\\, T\\, \\hat{\\mathbf{e}}_y,\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\nabla \\cdot \\mathbf{u} = 0,\n"
"\n"
"\\rho\\, c_p\\, (\\mathbf{u} \\cdot \\nabla T)\n"
"\\;=\\; \\kappa\\, \\Delta T,"
msgstr ""
"\\rho\\, (\\mathbf{u} \\cdot \\nabla)\\mathbf{u}\n"
"\\;=\\; -\\nabla p + \\mu\\, \\Delta \\mathbf{u}\n"
"- \\rho\\, g\\, \\beta\\, T\\, \\hat{\\mathbf{e}}_y,\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\nabla \\cdot \\mathbf{u} = 0,\n"
"\n"
"\\rho\\, c_p\\, (\\mathbf{u} \\cdot \\nabla T)\n"
"\\;=\\; \\kappa\\, \\Delta T,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:33
#: 994f237d1b6a4501977b7288b1eade93
msgid "on :math:`\\Omega = [0, 2] \\times [0, 1]`, with"
msgstr "定义在 :math:`\\Omega = [0, 2] \\times [0, 1]` 上，其中"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:35
#: 5bfc2113d43f4eca9cb8df57a6cab767
msgid "velocity: no-slip on all walls,"
msgstr "速度：所有壁面均为无滑移，"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:36
#: e3e4fa605dab4224a263478b7d22081d
msgid ""
"temperature: :math:`T = 1` on the bottom (:math:`y = 0`), :math:`T = 0` on "
"the top (:math:`y = 1`), no-flux on the side walls."
msgstr ""
"温度：底部（\\ :math:`y = 0`\\ ）为 :math:`T = 1`\\ ，顶部（\\ :math:`y = 1`\\ ）为 "
":math:`T = 0`\\ ，侧壁为无通量。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:40
#: 0a5587907a484a65ad5385d7e2748ac0
msgid "The Rayleigh number"
msgstr "瑞利数"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:42
#: fc5653bc084d475f985abc889e629226
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\mathrm{Ra} \\;=\\;\n"
"\\frac{g\\, \\beta\\, \\Delta T\\, L^3}{\\nu\\, \\alpha}"
msgstr ""
"\\mathrm{Ra} \\;=\\;\n"
"\\frac{g\\, \\beta\\, \\Delta T\\, L^3}{\\nu\\, \\alpha}"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:47
#: 5f8212886fa04a788bc9d5c5f97f658c
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"controls the regime: below :math:`\\mathrm{Ra}_c \\approx 1708` heat "
"transfer is purely conductive; above it convective rolls appear; at higher "
":math:`\\mathrm{Ra}` the rolls become unsteady and eventually chaotic. The "
"script defaults to :math:`\\mathrm{Ra} = 10^4`, comfortably in the steady-"
"convective regime."
msgstr ""
"决定了流动所处的区间：低于 :math:`\\mathrm{Ra}_c \\approx 1708` 时传热纯粹靠传导；高于此值则出现对流卷；在更高的 "
":math:`\\mathrm{Ra}` 下，卷会变得非定常并最终走向混沌。脚本默认取 :math:`\\mathrm{Ra} = 10^4`\\ "
"，稳稳地处于稳态对流区间。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:56
#: 60d99d733b5f4c42942db545e72d87d2
msgid "Coupled assembler"
msgstr "耦合装配器"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:58
#: c9b090fed4354a4e90ac60866ffdc9b7
msgid ""
"The unknowns at each node are :math:`(u, v, p, T)` — four DOFs per node — "
"and the assembler returns a :math:`4 \\times 4` block per quadrature point:"
msgstr ""
"每个节点上的未知量为 :math:`(u, v, p, T)`——每个节点 4 个自由度——装配器在每个求积点返回一个 :math:`4 \\times"
" 4` 的块："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:62
#: 5ebb203e14a84e00bed1c740d6503d63
msgid "examples/fluid/rayleigh_benard/rayleigh_benard.py (essence)"
msgstr "examples/fluid/rayleigh_benard/rayleigh_benard.py（核心部分）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:78
#: 1854b3ea45e448bab29bf50d30b1fce0
msgid ""
"The buoyancy block at row 1 / col 3 is what couples temperature back into "
"the momentum equation:"
msgstr "位于第 1 行 / 第 3 列的浮力块正是将温度反耦合进动量方程的部分："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:81
#: c2c8bfe00d944f27a84b9fefc8aabec8
#, python-brace-format
msgid "K_{1,3} \\;=\\; -\\rho\\, g\\, \\beta\\, v\\, u,"
msgstr "K_{1,3} \\;=\\; -\\rho\\, g\\, \\beta\\, v\\, u,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:85
#: cd04575ad6aa40109b31e35b0064a850
msgid ""
"where here :math:`u` and :math:`v` are the trial- and test-shape function "
"values (note the unfortunate name collision with the *velocity* :math:`v` "
"field — see :doc:`../../user_guide/forms` for the dispatch convention). The "
"temperature equation (row 3) re-uses the convection / diffusion block but "
"with thermal conductivity :math:`\\kappa` in place of viscosity "
":math:`\\mu`."
msgstr ""
"这里的 :math:`u` 与 :math:`v` 是试探形函数与测试形函数的值（请注意它们与\\ *速度*\\ 分量 :math:`v` "
"不幸的命名冲突——分发约定参见 :doc:`../../user_guide/forms`\\ ）。温度方程（第 3 行）复用了对流 / "
"扩散块，只是用热导率 :math:`\\kappa` 取代了黏度 :math:`\\mu`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:92
#: bbf6c288feb14b92af16bb3b8548f30a
msgid ""
"The previous-iterate velocity ``w_prev`` and temperature ``T_prev`` arrive "
"as ``point_data`` kwargs, exactly the same pattern as the single-physics "
"cavity example."
msgstr ""
"上一迭代步的速度 ``w_prev`` 与温度 ``T_prev`` 以 ``point_data`` "
"关键字参数的形式传入，模式与单物理场的方腔算例完全一致。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:98
#: 06d2c150064b42ce80e19ddb461e5ae9
msgid "Stabilization"
msgstr "稳定化"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:100
#: 9b967afb175d4ec88a90e151fd3821e3
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The script uses **PSPG only** (no SUPG), with a constant :math:`\\tau = 0.05"
" / n_\\text{grid}`. At :math:`\\mathrm{Ra} = 10^4` the velocities are mild "
"enough that SUPG is not strictly required; for higher Rayleigh numbers, swap"
" in the adaptive :math:`\\tau` from :doc:`cylinder_flow`."
msgstr ""
"脚本\\ **仅使用 PSPG**\\ （不含 SUPG），并取常数 :math:`\\tau = 0.05 / n_\\text{grid}`\\ "
"。在 :math:`\\mathrm{Ra} = 10^4` 下，速度足够温和，SUPG 并非严格必需；对于更高的瑞利数，可换用 "
":doc:`cylinder_flow` 中的自适应 :math:`\\tau`\\ 。"

