msgstr "由当前解向量计算 :math:`\\mathbf{w}^n, T^n`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:114
#: be968689b1b7438c8c0b393b0b023061
msgid "Reassemble :math:`K` with the new ``point_data``."
msgstr "用新的 ``point_data`` 重新装配 :math:`K`\\ 。"

