msgid ""
"Apply the :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` for the velocity and temperature "
"Dirichlet BCs (different masks per component!) and solve."
msgstr "对速度与温度的狄利克雷边界条件应用 :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser`\\ （每个分量使用不同的掩码！）并求解。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/rayleigh_benard.rst:118
